WEBVTT

00:03.210 --> 00:05.430
Sabrina, are you growling like a bear?

00:05.430 --> 00:07.070
I can't get this jar open.

00:07.070 --> 00:09.330
I'll do it, it's all in the wrist.

00:11.320 --> 00:12.980
Oh man, that's on tight.

00:13.160 --> 00:16.030
It looks like they're afraid the spaghetti sauce'll fall into the wrong hands.

00:16.030 --> 00:17.150
What's up?

00:17.150 --> 00:19.150
I can't get this jar open.

00:19.150 --> 00:20.540
Oh, don't you know the trick?

00:20.540 --> 00:24.940
Here, you whack it lightly to break the seal and there. uer!!

00:26.770 --> 00:28.790
See? It's not so easy.

00:28.790 --> 00:30.790
Well then, use magic.

00:30.790 --> 00:33.350
Good idea. The finger is mightier than the wrist.

00:37.060 --> 00:38.510
That should do it.

00:40.780 --> 00:43.100
what is wrong with this jar?!

00:43.100 --> 00:44.430
I give up.

00:46.070 --> 00:48.910
You know it's great having supernatural powers

00:48.910 --> 00:51.720
but for some things, we could really use a man around the house.

00:59.090 --> 01:01.830
1x20. Meeting Dad's Girlfriend

01:03.000 --> 01:09.074
